'flow' will be built mainly for demonstation and educational purpose

It may become possible to use 'flow' in closed or open networks such
as your local network or the internet.

Since 'flow' uses strong encryption and encryption might be illegal in
some countries, it is your repsonsibility to care for your local law.
Every user of this software and its documentation is encouraged to make
sure no law is being broken on his/her side.

The author(s) of this software will not take any responsibility for any
kind of usage of this software.
